            <div class="faq-a">Documentable distribution reductions for ASC reinvestment receive favorable treatment. We provide a letter of explanation documenting the reinvestment (typically Section 179 expensing on new ASC equipment) and the expected return to historical distribution levels. The 24-month average smooths the temporary reduction. Form 1084 cash-flow analysis at the ASC entity level adds back the non-cash equipment depreciation.</div>
