            <div class="faq-a">For the surgical practice: two years of Form 1120-S corporate returns with Schedule K-1s, Schedule L showing retained earnings. For each ASC partnership: 2 years of Form 1065 with K-1s and ownership documentation. Plus personal 1040 with all schedules. Plus all W-2s and 1099-NECs. Plus hospital employment contract or partnership agreement. Plus signed device consulting agreements if applicable. Plus IDR servicer statement. Plus ABMS board certification documentation. Plus state medical licensure.</div>
